      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://fortedward.net/about/history/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Fort Edward sits on the historic Great Carrying Place, a Native American portage that linked the Hudson River to Lake Champlain.",
